# Fullstack React + Node.js App on Kubernetes (Kind)

This project is a complete **fullstack application** containing:

- **Frontend** â†’ React app served using **Nginx**
- **Backend** â†’ Node.js + Express API
- **Kubernetes Deployment** â†’ Multi-container pod (frontend + backend)
- **Service** â†’ NodePort exposing frontend & backend to localhost
- **Kind (Kubernetes in Docker)** â†’ Local cluster

This repository is designed to help you build, containerize, deploy, and access a fullstack application using **Docker + Kubernetes + Kind**.

