# ğŸš€ Features

- React frontend served by Nginx
- Node.js backend with REST endpoints
- Multi-container Kubernetes Pods
- NodePort service exposing frontend (30080) + backend (30081)
- Local Kind cluster (Docker-based)
- Production-ready Dockerfiles (multi-stage for frontend)

